the easiest way is a 1917 american silent film starring clara kimball young and directed by albert capellani . it is based on a 1909 play , the easiest way by eugene walter , staged by david belasco and starred frances starr as laura murdock . belasco and starr revived the play in 1921 . it is not known whether the film currently survives . actor joseph kilgour reprises his role as brockton from the broadway play .